title: Are You Their Ride or Die ( Yung Bleu interview )
itunes:title: Are You Their Ride or Die ( Yung Bleu interview )
description:
Today on the show we had Yung Bleu stop by where he spoke about Loyalty, Linking With Drake, Tory Lanez, New Music and More. Also they opened up the phone lines to if our listeners are a ride or die in a relationship after the proposal with Michael Blackson and his girlfriend this week, And Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a trump supporter who spent $30 Million Building The ‘Lamborghini’ Of Border Walls, And Now, He Desperately Needs Someone To Buy It.
